15,01;---------------------------------------------------
15,01 Description of lines
15,011  Sysop name
15,012  header ansi/pcb file, do not include path.  Put NONE for no header
15,013  put YES if you want to use faster line clearing (you can't use borders), othe
15,01rwise it uses slower space fillings to clear lines allowing borders, also allows
15,01 vertically aligned windows.
15,014  Top window text color
15,015  Bottom window text color
15,016  # of lines to leave displayed at top when scrolling up
15,017  Position data for top window's id line
15,01   xx,yy:len  xx = xpos  yy = ypos  len = justified len of user name in OPTEXT
15,018  Data line for top window's id, put @OPTEXT@ in for the name
15,019  Position data for bottom window's id line  (same format as above)
15,0110 Data line for bottom window's id, put @OPTEXT@ in for the name
15,0111 Top Line # (1-23) for Top window
15,0112 # of lines for Top window (1-10)
15,0113 Min-Max horizontal value (1-78) for Top window line 1
15,01   repeat this for however many lines are setup, or you will get errors in the
15,01   chatter if not repeated the right # of times
15,0114 Top Line # (1-23) for Bottom window
15,0115 # of lines for Bottom Window (1-10)
15,0116 Min-Max horizontal value (1-78) for Bot window line 1
15,01   repeat this for however many lines are setup
15,01>
